name: Fertilization / Ovum X-Ray (work in progress)
description:
This is more of a proof of concept while I mentally prepare for the arduous labor of cleaning out the training data.

Just use the activation tag, depending on the other models in use a weight of 1 should be fine. Works much more reliably if the prompt specifies a character (even just 1girl should suffice).

Creates the effect (ovum in the process of fertilization) like 50% of the time, although some of those times look desireable while others just create weird fake x-ray's. They also end up holding their ovum in hand a lot which ??? but oh well.

Will definitely work on this to polish it up in the future.
